tossup_question: -   –  What is the equation of the plane, parallel to one of the coordinate planes, that passes through the two points (4,7,-2) and (3,7,12)?
bonus_question: -   –  If all A are B and some C are A, identify all of the following three conclusions that necessarily follow: 1) All A are C; 2) Some B are C; 3) Some A are not C.
